<div id="content">

    
        	    





		
										

        


                
                	    

    
    
        	    





		
										

        


    
        

        <div id="article-wrapper" class="trackable-component"          	        data-component="Article:in body link">

        	
        	
    <div id="article-body-blocks">
	    <p>Thanks for all your suggestions on <a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/sport/blog/2013/apr/27/gifs-spain-euro-crisis-muhammad-ali">our last week's blog</a>. Here are a few highlights from this week.</p><h2>Dodgeboys</h2><p><img src="http://img838.imageshack.us/img838/4599/fortuna2.gif" width="460" height="276"/></p><p>Roy Jones Jr. shows how to <a href="http://s3.amazonaws.com/rapgenius/1355446594_297886_o.gif">duck, bob, weave and dive</a>.</p><p>Beyond boxing, Anderson Silva is the master of shuffling his body away from oncoming fists: Exhibits <a href="http://cdn3.sbnation.com/imported_assets/790001/jpuh7c_jpg.gif">A</a>, <a href="http://cdn1.sbnation.com/imported_assets/508294/silvashuffle.gif">B</a> and <a href="http://www.cagedinsider.com/images/Anderson-bonnar.gif">C</a>.</p><h2>Team bonding</h2><p><img src="http://img.thesun.co.uk/multimedia/archive/01716/kneerub_1716315a.gif" width="460" height="276"/></p><p>Which is worse: overfamiliarity or <a href="http://coedbc.files.wordpress.com/2013/04/1008mef.gif?w=494&amp;h=275">blatant rudeness</a>?</p><h2>One motion, five pitches</h2><p><img src="http://cdn.bleacherreport.net/images_root/article/media_slots/photos/000/829/207/b0fe05cc-7813-45d0-a71e-5dc564c3c7ae_DarvishPitch_original.jpg?1366919618" width="460" height="276"/></p><p><a href="http://l1.yimg.com/bt/api/res/1.2/jIxPBrRzVqoU_1q2aegKvQ--/YXBwaWQ9eW5ld3M7cT04NTt3PTQ3MA--/http://l.yimg.com/os/publish-images/sports/2013-04-17/09c11f31-e9a2-44e4-a81b-be73b6efaa94_ShoppachThrow.gif">How not to throw a baseball</a>. This one <a href="http://www.terezowens.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/wukd-out-c.gif">isn't much better</a>. </p><p>In other baseball news, this fan <a href="http://d3fsqtc6sy2z27.cloudfront.net/uploads/77f777956738a00bc25232f392c9f51d_large">fields better than he dances</a>. </p><h2>Schoolboy defending</h2><p><img src="http://paddypowerblog.files.wordpress.com/2013/04/blog_the-worst-pt2.gif?w=610" width="460" height="276"/></p><p><a href="http://cdn.bleacherreport.net/social_assets/nfl/Week_2/Browns_Bengals/TrentRichardson_BeastMode.gif">An NFL equivalent</a>. This is how to <a href="http://d3j5vwomefv46c.cloudfront.net/photos/large/755904500.gif">defend properly</a>.</p><h2>Face off</h2><p><img src="http://cdn0.sbnation.com/imported_assets/1484413/staalface_medium.gif" width="460" height="276"/></p><p>Tyson Fury <a href="http://img.thesun.co.uk/multimedia/archive/01715/boxer_1715948a.gif">uppercuts himself</a>, a brave volunteer gets <a href="http://img.thesun.co.uk/multimedia/archive/01716/ball_1716309a.gif">his comeuppance</a> and one <a href="http://thenewsportsguru.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/dude-eats-it.gif">poor fan falls on his face</a>.</p><h2>Miami coach Jim Larranaga knows how to move</h2><p><img src="http://cdnl.complex.com/assets/CHANNEL_IMAGES/SPORTS/2013/03/content/1364185454_larranga.gif" width="460" height="276"/></p><p>If only <a href="https://s3.amazonaws.com/assets.stippleit.com/photos/46831130/original/iba2kJ7uos4ywx.gif?1364189087%22%22">fans were equally gifted</a>.</p><h2>King David Luiz</h2><p><img src="http://cdn2.mocksession.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/LUIZ.gif" width="460" height="276"/></p><p><strong>Drop your favourites into the comments box below and we'll be back with some more next week</strong></p>
    </div>

						
	
		
            	    





		
										

        


        </div>
    
    
                
